    <div class="container">
        <h1>Sonic Drive-In Happy Hour</h1>
        <p><a href="https://sonicmnu.com/happy-hour-menu/">Sonic Drive-In's Happy Hour</a> is a daily event that offers customers the opportunity to enjoy a variety of beverages and snacks at discounted prices. Taking place from <span class="highlight">2:00 PM to 4:00 PM</span>, this special time is perfect for those looking to indulge in refreshing drinks and tasty treats without stretching their budget.</p>
        
        <h2>Half-Price Drinks and Slushes</h2>
        <p>During Happy Hour, Sonic offers a wide selection of drinks and slushes at half their regular prices. This includes classic soft drinks, iced teas, lemonades, limeades, and their famous slushes in flavors like Cherry, Blue Raspberry, and Watermelon.</p>
        
        <h2>Discounted Snacks</h2>
        <p>In addition to beverages, select snacks are also offered at reduced prices during Happy Hour. Favorites like Corn Dogs, Mozzarella Sticks, Onion Rings, and Tater Tots are available to satisfy your mid-afternoon cravings.</p>
        
        <h2>Late Night Deals</h2>
        <p>Some Sonic locations extend their specials into the evening with <span class="highlight">Late Night Happy Hours</span> starting at 8:00 PM until closing. During these hours, customers can enjoy half-price shakes, including flavors like Vanilla, Chocolate, and Strawberry.</p>
        
        <h2>All-Day Deals via the Sonic App</h2>
        <p>For those who can't make it during designated Happy Hours, the Sonic App offers an alternative. By ordering through the app, customers can access half-price drinks and slushes all day long.</p>
        
